  1. Try the benchmark methods.
autoplot(temp.ts) +
autolayer(meanf(temp.ts, h=50),
series="Mean", PI=FALSE) +
autolayer(naive(temp.ts, h=50),
series="Nave", PI=FALSE) +
autolayer(rwf(temp.ts, drift=TRUE, h=50),
series="Drift", PI=FALSE) +
ggtitle("Benchmark Models vs Model") +
xlab("Days") + ylab("") +
guides(colour=guide_legend(title="Forecast"))
